GENDER SLEEP GAP//
Women experience higher activity in regions of the brain associated with impulse control, anxiety, and mood. During sleep, these parts of the brain disengage and recover, which can take longer for women, requiring more time spent in deep sleep.

Sleepy Mag is magnesium glycinate and a microdose of plant-based melatonin to help you fall and stay asleep, without the AM hangover.
